&lt;li&gt;In-house experience at a technology company, or law firm experience advising tech clients on regulatory investigations or enforcement matters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with AI systems, machine learning concepts, or experience advising on novel technology products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
